4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with in-demand skills in technologies like JavaScript and Python. Over 18 weeks, participants attend three classes weekly in small groups (1 instructor per 7 students). The program has no prerequisites and is available in English and Spanish. Students will engage in hands-on projects, culminating in a self-developed project. Successful completion grants a Full-Stack Developer certificate. The course prepares individuals for a career in tech, emphasizing the importance of programming, logic, and research skills. For further details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop